        <div>
          <p class="text-xs font-mono tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-[#8B7A3A] mb-2">November–December 2023,  Roof frame and tiles</p>
          <p class="text-lg font-light text-[#2C2824]/85 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The roof frame was the only phase where we brought in an outside company. Trusses assembled in modules on site, crane-lifted by truck and set on the walls. It went fast.
