          <p class="text-sm font-light text-black/50 max-w-lg">Timber framing of partitions before closing; the space takes shape, the lots become clear.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-[680px] mx-auto px-10 sm:px-16 lg:px-24">
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-light text-[#2C2824]/85 leading-relaxed">
        The building knows who it's for. After the explosion of 2023, the silence of 2024 and the metamorphosis of 2025, Grand Shambala is no longer a project. It's a place.
